^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let's discuss the bidding. A very important bidding principle is "support with support." Sometimes with a good hand and 3-card support, you can’t support right away, but on this auction, Boater's 1N followed by 2S showed exactly 2 spades. The reason being, with a weak hand and 3-card support, she should bid 2S right away. |
